Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.59,0:24:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs50\pos(200,320)\bord0\blur1}{\fn方正大标宋_GBK}人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.17,0:24:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！！又回来了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.95,0:24:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的距离在缩短
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.67,0:24:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的心灵在走远
